# Heap-use-after-free in TrackRegistry::ResetForTesting (third_party/perfetto).
# ResetForTesting clears the tracks_ map without holding the mutex while
# UpdateTrack on a worker thread accesses it under the mutex. This is a real
# race in upstream Perfetto code only detected under ASan.
# Stable upstream (0.0% flake rate, 160K runs over 30 days per LUCI Analysis).
# https://github.com/brave/brave-browser/issues/55579
-TracingScenarioTest.SpuriousStop
